Component.Description:
Defines the dimensions of a box shape by the relative offset of two opposite corners. A box of
max=Vector3(1,1,1) and min=Vector3(-1,-1,-1) will result in a 2x2x2 box. This is to be used with
the `mesh://box` `Mesh` URI.

@property min The relative offset of the bottom corner (furthest in the -x, -y, -z direction)
@property max The relative offset of the top corner (furthest in the +x, +y, +z direction)
